---
- error: PRIMARY KEY missing on table T3
...
box.sql.execute("CREATE TABLE t4(a, b)")
---
- error: PRIMARY KEY missing on table T4
...
box.sql.execute("CREATE TABLE t5(a, b UNIQUE)")
---
- error: PRIMARY KEY missing on table T5
